rget=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104svf1665702769463.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/svf1665702769463.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/svf1665702769463.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"svf1665702769463\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Assignments for Remote Services and Reports\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"svf1665702769463__assignments_for_remote_services_and_reports_98731\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Assignments in the sections [SERVICES_EXEC] and [REPORTS_EXEC] direct the execution of each service or report component to a Uniface Server specified in the [PATHS] section.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"svf1665702769463__p_d30287e1_d30288e1_d30289e1\">The path can specify a TCP/IP or TLS network path.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"svf1665702769463__section_fhn_vfv_qcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d173281e56\">Example: Services and Reports on TCP/IP Path</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, the client assignment file directs services and reports to a\n            network path $NET1. This path opens a TCP connection to the host machine HOST1, where\n            the Uniface Router uses the UST (server name) <code class=\"ph codeph\">ASV</code> to start a Uniface\n            Server (an application server instance) using the assignment file\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">asv.asn</span>. The application server then locates the services and\n            reports on the local file system.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"svf1665702769463__pre_gfj_wfv_qcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; Client assignment file\n[PATHS]\n$NET1 = TCP:HOST1|?|?|ASV\n[SERVICES_EXEC]\n* = $NET1:*\n[REPORTS_EXEC]\n* = $NET1:*\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The Uniface Router on HOST1 uses the server name ASV to start an application server\n            instance using the assignment file <span class=\"ph filepath\">asv.asn</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"svf1665702769463__pre_hfj_wfv_qcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; urouter.asn - Uniface Router assignment file on HOST1\n[SERVERS]\nASV = userver.exe /asn=asv.asn\nDATA = userver.exe /asn=data.asn\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Assignments in the [ENTITIES] and [RESOURCES] sections of the application server’s\n            assignment file <span class=\"ph filepath\">asv.asn</span> direct entities to a data server on HOST1\n            (not shown in example) and services and reports to UAR files on the local file\n            system.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"svf1665702769463__pre_ifj_wfv_qcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; asv.asn - ASV assignment file on HOST1\n[PATHS]\n$NET2 = TCP:HOST1|kaye|birdbrain|DATA\n[ENTITIES]\n*.* = $NET2:*.*\n[RESOURCES]\nd:/unifiles/services.uar\nd:/unifiles/reports.uar\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532186\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Assignments for Remote Services and Reports Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Assignments for Remote Services and Reports Assignments in the sections [SERVICES_EXEC] and [REPORTS_EXEC] direct the execution of each service or report component to a Uniface Server specified in the [PATHS] section. The path can specify a TCP/IP or TLS network path. Example: Services and Reports on TCP/IP Path In the following example, the client assignment file directs services and reports to a network path $NET1. This path opens a TCP connection to the host machine HOST1, where the Uniface Router uses the UST (server name) ASV to start a Uniface Server (an application server instance) using the assignment file asv.asn . The application server then locates the services and reports on the local file system. ; Client assignment file [PATHS] $NET1 = TCP:HOST1|?|?|ASV [SERVICES_EXEC] * = $NET1:* [REPORTS_EXEC] * = $NET1:* Copy The Uniface Router on HOST1 uses the server name ASV to start an application server instance using the assignment file asv.asn . ; urouter.asn - Uniface Router assignment file on HOST1 [SERVERS] ASV = userver.exe /asn=asv.asn DATA = userver.exe /asn=data.asn Copy Assignments in the [ENTITIES] and [RESOURCES] sections of the application server’s assignment file asv.asn direct entities to a data server on HOST1 (not shown in example) and services and reports to UAR files on the local file system. ; asv.asn - ASV assignment file on HOST1 [PATHS] $NET2 = TCP:HOST1|kaye|birdbrain|DATA [ENTITIES] *.* = $NET2:*.* [RESOURCES] d:/unifiles/services.uar d:/unifiles/reports.uar Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}